data.description: GOLFER'S DREAM HOME on the 9th hole!!  Stunning custom home with resort style pool & backyard located in sought after Lake Windcrest!!  This amazing property awaits its new homeowners with quality construction & high end interior finishes like travertine & wood flooring, gorgeous kitchen with endless counter space & built-in Kitchen Aid refrigerator, wine grotto, primary bath with huge steam shower, upstairs theater room & SO much more!!!    Lush landscaping, outdoor kitchen, inviting pool, huge covered patio...make this backyard perfect for entertaining.    THIS IS A MUST SEE!!
